parameters.name: ImageFamily
parameters.description: The name of the image family. The name must be 2 to 128 characters in length and can contain letters, digits, colons (:), underscores (\_), and hyphens (-). It must start with a letter and cannot start with http://, https://, acs:, or aliyun.

parameters.name: RegionId
parameters.description: The region ID of the image. You can call the [DescribeRegions](~~25609~~) operation to query the most recent region list.
